{
  "stem": "7069.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And so-- and so then I found out that all the synagogues have-- during that night, also, about 35 Jewish men were killed.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Among them rabbis that tried to defend their synagogues, as well as about-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] --30,000 Jewish men were rounded up during that night.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at that moment I went on, then, to my-- to my workplace, of course.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there-- there we talked a little bit about that there was another couple of Jewish apprentices where I was too.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so we talked about that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And well, we were wondering what happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We couldn't put together, at this point.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then later on, of course, next day or so, then we knew what happened all over the places.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the Kristallnacht is considered to be the beginning of the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A prelude, as it were, of the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From that time on, out of Germany, regularly, Jews were picked up during the nights and were sent to the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see, Hitler built already, the first concentration camps-- camp only two months after he was in power.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Dachau, near Munich.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then from then on, there-- they grew up like mushrooms, all over the places.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, pretty soon friends disappeared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And family members disappeared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Neighbors disappeared.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was interesting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In-- in our building that we lived, there were a couple of other Jewish families.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody ever asked what happened to these or what happened to those.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so people sort of accepted it or didn't dare to-- to-- to ask or talk about it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because of course, pretty soon this state, Hitler's state had developed into a dictatorship, particularly due to the fact that all other political parties-- and they were up to 30 at times-- were outlawed, were not allowed to operate.",
      "word_count": 39
    }
  ],
